14556-/// identical tokenizer, then read the emitted token instances back via the
14557-/// `fts5vocab(..., 'instance')` companion. The token multiset is returned in
14558-/// index order (duplicates kept) so callers count tf and field length directly.
14559-/// Query terms and every candidate field go through this one path, so all four
14560-/// statistics are consistent with each other and with the FTS5 index the scorer
